title: Steve Wilkos Mommy I Keep Getting Raped
description:
MOMMY I KEEP GETTING RAPED:

    One of Steve's most intense episodes! Laney's daughter was taken away from her 2 years ago because her daughter was molested by 7 different men and she knew about it the entire time! Steve can't understand how any parent would ever let that happen. Laney wanted to come to the show to see her daughter, but Steve doesn't think that Laney deserves to see her daughter. Laney's ex-relative has been taking care of Laney's daughter and will not let Laney ever see her daughter again
